	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002188_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'-->
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>11 Feby 1865 </p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Alington</persName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>The box referred to 
<lb/>in your note is 
<lb/>probably one of four 
<lb/>sent away from 
<lb/><placeName>Mozambique</placeName> without 
<lb/>any address by the 
<lb/>late <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Burrup</persName>. 
<lb/>They belonged to <persName>D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi>
<lb/>Kirk</persName> and they were 
<lb/>entrusted to M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Rae 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002188_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'-->
<lb/>and to be addressed 
<lb/>by him at <placeName>Quillimane</placeName>
<lb/>he had neglected to do 
<lb/>so &amp; <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Burrup</persName>
<lb/>finding them after
<lb/>wards at <placeName>Mosambique</placeName>
<lb/>sent them off some 
<lb/>where<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>After communicating 
<lb/>with the Admiralty 
<lb/>I think you had 
<lb/>better send it to the 
<lb/>"<placeName>Royal Botanic 
<lb/>Gardens</placeName>" <placeName>Kew</placeName>
<lb/><placeName>London</placeName>
<lb/><choice><reg>A</reg><orig>a</orig></choice>nd I shall write 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002188_0003"/><!--pb/@n='3'-->
<lb/>to have it identified 
<lb/>Address it please to 
<lb/><persName>D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> J. D. Hooker</persName>, there. 
<lb/>By attending to this 
<lb/>you will much 
<lb/>oblige. Yours ever </p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I think I told you 
<lb/>that I am going 
<lb/>out again as soon 
<lb/>as this book is out<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">Did you hear of any 
<lb/>other boxes belong to 
<lb/>the expedition? 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Young</persName> brought 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002188_0004"/><!--pb/@n='4'-->
<lb/>all <persName>Thornton<reg>'</reg>s</persName> boxes 
<lb/>in his charge &amp; 
<lb/>reported them to me 
<lb/>as safe at <placeName>Portsmouth</placeName>
<lb/>long ago<reg>.</reg></p>
			
</div>
